title: Former Obama-Era U.S. Ambassador Calls for Hungary to Be Expelled from EU
description: Former United States Ambassador to the United Nations Susan Rice has called for Hungary to be expelled from the European Union after the country passed emergency measures to combat the Wuhan coronavirus.
